  "text": "In the Netherlands, while SER has been influential in the past, there is not much reference to it anymore. In school improvement, projects are announced or sold as evidence-based that actually do not meet the criteria [CITATION_1] . SER has, however, been important in the evaluation scheme used by the Inspectorate and the emphasis given on student learning outcomes.",
